{"prompt": "Generate a website for a professional law firm. The website should be playful and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Justice & Merriment Law</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #e0f2f7; /* Lightest blue */\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #0077cc; /* Brand blue */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #005fa3; /* Darker blue */\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .section p {\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .services-list {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: #f0f8ff; /* Very light blue */\n            border: 1px solid #0077cc; /* Brand blue border */\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin: 10px;\n            width: 30%;\n           